title: President of Republic receives EU High Representative for Foreign Affairs and Security Policy
text: The President of the Republic, Abdelmadjid Tebboune received Monday at the Presidency of the Republic, the High Representative of the European Union (EU) for Foreign Affairs and Security Policy and Vice-President of the European Commission, Josep Borrell, who is visiting Algeria.

The President of the Republic also had a working lunch on Monday in Algiers with the High Representative of the European Union (EU) for Foreign Affairs and Security Policy and Vice-President of the European Commission.
